 status of entry:
  • 0 => no programs are accessing,

  • n<0 => one program writing, 1+n reading.

guint32 access [2]
 date and time of last access in packed format (Packed years since 1900):
  • access[0] = 256 * (256 * YY + MM) + DD
  • access[1] = 256 * (256 * HH + MM) + SS
